<div class=WordSection1>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>Chapter 342</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>1997 EDITION</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>Teachers and Other School Personnel</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>TEACHERS AND OTHER SCHOOL PERSONNEL</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>EDUCATION AND CULTURAL FACILITIES</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>LICENSING OF TEACHERS</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>AND ADMINISTRATORS</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>(Generally)</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.120           Definitions</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.121           Teacher and administrator licensing;
certification from professional organizations; certificate not required</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.123           Knowledge of civil rights laws
required</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.125           Types of licenses; expedited process</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>Note    Subject matter indorsement--1993 c.45 s.154</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.126           First aid card required for teaching
license; waiver for disability</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.127           Fees; basis</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.130           Certain existing certificates not
invalidated</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.135           Basic, standard and other teaching
licenses; basis of renewal</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.136           Initial teaching, personnel service
and administrative licenses; renewal</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.138           Continuing teaching, personnel service
and administrative licenses; qualifications for continuing license</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.140           Administrative license</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.143           Qualifications for teaching or
administrative license</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.147           Approval of teacher education
institutions and programs</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.153           Proficiency in Braille required for
teaching license to provide education to blind students</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.165           Commission rules</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.167           State board review of rules</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.169           Required ratio of pupils to staff
holders of first aid cards; exceptions</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.173           Effect of employing unlicensed teacher
or administrator by certain districts</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>(Discipline)</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.175           Grounds for discipline; reinstatement</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.176           Preliminary investigation of
complaint; materials confidential; notice whether hearing justified</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.177           Hearing and decision on charges</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.180           Appeal</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.190           Administrative Procedure Act not
applicable to proceedings for reinstatement, revocation or suspension</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>(Miscellaneous)</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.195           Teaching licenses based on experience
in certain federal programs</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.200           Administrative licenses based on
professional skills and experience</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>342.203           Circulation of list of teachers and
administrators subjected to discipline</span></p>

