line-height:12.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>            342.617</span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:-.15pt'> [1985 c.585 s.2; 1993 c.45
s.184; renumbered 332.554 in 1993]</span></p>

