line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:-.15pt'>            342.663</span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:-.15pt'> [1969 c.266 ss.1, 2, 3; 1993
c.45 s.186; renumbered 332.544 in 1993]</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:12.0pt'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
